kiss of death is a 1995 crime american thriller film starring david caruso , samuel l. jackson , nicolas cage , helen hunt , ving rhames , and stanley tucci , directed by barbet schroeder . the film is a very loosely based remake of the 1947 film noir classic of the same name that starred victor mature , brian donlevy , and richard widmark . it was screened out of competition at the 1995 cannes film festival . like the original kiss of death , the film was released by 20th century fox .